exercise.instructions:
After the @TEMPLATE@_ResetAppCmd() function protoype definition add the @TEMPLATE@_SetParamCmd() definition:
  bool @TEMPLATE@_SetParamCmd(void *ObjDataPtr, const CFE_MSG_Message_t *MsgPtr);
  This isn't required to compile the code, but is good practice if teh function needs to be access by a unit test.

After the last CMDMGR_RegisterFunc() add
  CMDMGR_RegisterFunc(CMDMGR_OBJ, @TEMPLATE@_SET_PARAM_CC, NULL, @TEMPLATE@_SetParamCmd, sizeof(@TEMPLATE@_SetParamCmd_Payload_t));
  Note @TEMPLATE@_SET_PARAM_CMD_CC is generated by the EDS toolchain
